users

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • users.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a single user who wants to connect to the server. Each user holds several attribute needed to play a game.
    Author:
    Stefan Fuchs, Jan-Niklas Wortmann
    See Also:
